{"tid":1070000,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"駭人！馬來西亞河川遭傾倒劇毒廢棄物 逾2700人病倒","createTime":"2019-03-20T10:39:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T13:32:02.000Z","uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bee6d3d79d1376a3fd30c15ed54c64f7f1e4b418","tid":1070000,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T10:39:00.000Z","msg":"恐怖！馬來西亞柔佛州工業城巴西古當（Pasir Gudang）的一條小河流，遭非法份子傾倒20<br />\n噸至40噸的劇毒廢棄物，導致當地超過2700人病倒。<br />\n<br />\n據《CNN》報導，這條在馬來文裡被稱為Sungai Kim Kim的河川，只有1.6公里長。載滿廢棄<br />\n物的卡車於3月6日非法傾倒後，光是7日1天便有35人吸進有毒氣體而送醫，其中大部分都是<br />\n在附近上學的學生。<br />\n<br />\n當局發現狀況不對後，8日召集專業人員穿著防護服前往協助。當地環境部官員沙烈（<br />\nMohammad Ezzani Mat Salleh）率領團隊勘查後，發現小河部分區域遭船用引擎的有毒廢油<br />\n汙染，另外還驗出至少15種不同類型的化學品，其中包括無色和極毒的氰化氫（hydrogen<br />\ncyanide）。<br />\n<br />\n受害者的數量不斷增加，短短一週之內就有超過2700人生病，症狀包括噁心、呼吸急促與嘔<br />\n吐，數百人立即被送往醫院治療。截至今天（20日）為止，還有2名病患在加護病房觀察。<br />\n<br />\n此次案件中學童受影響最嚴重，約有111所學校無限期關閉。馬來西亞教育部長馬利克（<br />\nMaszlee Malik）表示，尚無法確認何時才能重新開放學校。<br />\n<br />\n大馬當局已著手進行復原工作，但河川又赫然出現新的廢棄物，很有可能是非法份子趁著夜<br />\n間於岸邊傾倒。馬來西亞警方目前已逮捕9名涉案人士，一旦罪名成立，他們將面臨最高5年<br />\n有期徒刑與50萬令吉（約新台幣378萬元）的罰款。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php5nrjZn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php5nrjZn.jpg&h=e09d3ac2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3bfeb966c2a29f8bf91641841911088f1259f047","tid":1070000,"uid":86928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T10:44:10.000Z","msg":"倒20噸劇毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾佢吹漲唔知講咩好"},{"pid":"6c7879c8e5a4d198b9289cb4db55cfe4b8b59785","tid":1070000,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T10:49:10.000Z","msg":"HCN<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b8439182a25ebfb4e287ea51e565acd25fff264","tid":1070000,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T11:00:26.000Z","msg":"<code>\n馬來西亞警方目前已逮捕9名涉案人士，一旦罪名成立，他們將面臨最高5年\n有期徒刑與50萬令吉（約新台幣378萬元）的罰款。\n</code><br />\n<br />\nwow多謝喎"},{"pid":"5a6d6f44c72ce717adf4eef5f29281a35e0cf6d5","tid":1070000,"uid":39871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T11:02:56.000Z","msg":"5年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70cecde136f963f69d21fbf0492b2a8fb1cb46ac","tid":1070000,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T13:16:36.000Z","msg":"流落去新加坡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abae32a94bbe74fb6155c164f610be8e2a50dc0d","tid":1070000,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T13:18:45.000Z","msg":"痴撚線HCN就咁倒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89d80b6222e46303e3a8896c13b440c4842934db","tid":1070000,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T13:23:37.000Z","msg":"好似成個禮拜前"},{"pid":"f2543e6168a41f719077ddb18ff047d7b1bfe560","tid":1070000,"uid":30510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T13:32:02.000Z","msg":"環保組織呢"}]}